data.description: Beautiful & spacious are just a couple of words to describe this four-bedroom, 2 bath home in Rimes Ranch! This lovely property features over 2400 sq ft, a brand new roof, new carpet, new interior paint, an eat-in kitchen, granite countertops, double ovens, stainless steel appliances, a huge, walk-in pantry, and an oversized living area with a fireplace. The master bedroom offers a walk-in closet, a separate shower & jetted bath, a ceiling fan, and a double (separate) vanity. The privacy-fenced backyard and patio are perfect for those lovely fall evenings when the weather must be enjoyed. If you're still on the hunt for your next home, make this a must-stop and see! Schedule your tour today!
